          %p.text-p-xlarge.mb-20
            This month for #12in23 we're exploring languages that do things differently. We're digging into Ballerina, Pharo, Prolog, Red, Tcl and Unison, with interviews and live streaming, exclusive swag and lots of fun exercises for you to complete!

          .shadow-baseZ1.grid.grid-cols-2.gap-20.py-20.px-20.rounded-8.bg-white
